➜【星连文学社】听尘居士：无题
http://www.sohu.com/a/411826729_100115135	43461
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200806/b4fc7e8a944d425aa407d1ac55953a82.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/听尘居士</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不将流言付诗长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋来冬近知何方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">庄生晓梦蝶化远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风历千秋舞断肠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200806/38059c94a5d24da8b0c3b8380d639239.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>听尘居士，原名牛喜忠。吉林籍，现居深圳。半生无所成，流浪江湖。偶弄笔墨，未有一名。闲了拈花惹草，迎来半院春色；静时参禅打坐，佛道一通乱修。朋友小聚可品香茗，饮自酿美酒，临厨而成美食。唯不懂人间烟火，只好浪迹天涯一隅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/d07997667eca4a68be09db8493dd2ca5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
