http://www.sohu.com/a/411828108_100115135	43925
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/a5ce6532739149539b9fbadbe29b2f25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《梦赤壁》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/青衣小生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦回故地意未尽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云吞火海东风来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">过江赤壁尘飞远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铜雀安得美人怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200806/373e40db81014332a60753926a5c0be1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
