➜【星连文学社】广东诗人辉哥：偶得（词韵）
http://www.sohu.com/a/411828960_100115135	44334
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200806/eebe1a8f5490450cb2ffa598ef60e64c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>偶得（词韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风起天凉日渐西，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落英逐水两迷离；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一场暮雨千般绪，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无寄情怀入梦思。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/c854a6de34c34a159c8dda2086378fbd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>围炉诗情辉哥，来自广东梅县客家，自小在客家农村长大，对客家文化情有独钟。喜爱古诗词，涂鸦作品多用于自耍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200806/4a7cc8f7ce6c48c4a3d5faf6d0e598ac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
