➜【星连文学社】苏坛：《西津渡》
http://www.sohu.com/a/411829555_100115135	44575
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200806/88b20c21b7de4420a79adcae1906da5d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《西津渡》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在烟火气中想起了历史的硝烟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在波涛声里听见了诗的缠绵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在灯光下舞一曲哀伤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在渡口边叙一段离别</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你相伴着长江水东流</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你写下了多少的春花秋月</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你走过了千万的过客</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你让一线江天从未亘古</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我迷恋你古朴繁华的街巷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我感伤你曾经遭遇的屈辱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我沉浸在你走过的岁月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我动情你拥有的英雄和凤流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/3d45914053304d7d95a1219969708b79.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
